To create modules-$ARCH.sfs:
	* load an Ubuntu Live CD
	* install VirtualBox
	* install VirtualBox Guest Additions:
		- mount VBoxGuestAdditions.iso, run VBoxLinuxAdditions.run
	* cp -a /lib/{firmware,modules}
	* [x86] http://wireless.kernel.org/en/users/Drivers/b43 -> list of firmware -> b43legacy
	* [x86] copy b43legacy to /lib/modules/firmware/
	* ln -s /cdrom/secret /lib/modules/
	* install NVidia drivers:
		- Ctrl-Alt-F1, service stop lightdm, run NVIDIA-Linux-$ARCH-???.??.run
		- save userspace files to http://sigaev.com/programs/nvidia-$ARCH
	* mksquashfs /lib/modules modules-$ARCH.sfs -comp xz
